==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unfinished
<hw>Un*fin"ished</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not finished, not
brought to an end; imperfect; incomplete; left in the rough; wanting the
last hand or touch; <as>as, an <ex>unfinished</ex> house; an
<ex>unfinished</ex> picture; an <ex>unfinished</ex> iron
casting.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unfirm</ent>⟦br⟧
